                Get example projects source code from <a href="https://github.com/gabrysbiz/${project.name}-examples">GitHub</a>
                or download binaries from <a href="http://easy-bundle.projects.gabrys.biz/examples/">gabrys.biz</a>.
            </p>
        </section>
